<Link id="l00044" /><CodeLine lineNumber="44"><Highlight kind="comment">/// tryAddingSymbolicOperand - tryAddingSymbolicOperand trys to add a symbolic</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00045" /><CodeLine lineNumber="45"><Highlight kind="comment">/// operand in place of the immediate Value in the MCInst.  The immediate</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00046" /><CodeLine lineNumber="46"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Value has not had any PC adjustment made by the caller. If the instruction</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00047" /><CodeLine lineNumber="47"><Highlight kind="comment">/// is a branch that adds the PC to the immediate Value then isBranch is</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00048" /><CodeLine lineNumber="48"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Success, else Fail. If GetOpInfo is non-null, then it is called to get any</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00049" /><CodeLine lineNumber="49"><Highlight kind="comment">/// symbolic information at the Address for this instrution.  If that returns</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00050" /><CodeLine lineNumber="50"><Highlight kind="comment">/// non-zero then the symbolic information it returns is used to create an</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00051" /><CodeLine lineNumber="51"><Highlight kind="comment">/// MCExpr and that is added as an operand to the MCInst.  If GetOpInfo()</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00052" /><CodeLine lineNumber="52"><Highlight kind="comment">/// returns zero and isBranch is Success then a symbol look up for</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00053" /><CodeLine lineNumber="53"><Highlight kind="comment">/// Address + Value is done and if a symbol is found an MCExpr is created with</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00054" /><CodeLine lineNumber="54"><Highlight kind="comment">/// that, else an MCExpr with Address + Value is created.  If GetOpInfo()</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00055" /><CodeLine lineNumber="55"><Highlight kind="comment">/// returns zero and isBranch is Fail then the Opcode of the MCInst is</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00056" /><CodeLine lineNumber="56"><Highlight kind="comment">/// tested and for ADRP an other instructions that help to load of pointers</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00057" /><CodeLine lineNumber="57"><Highlight kind="comment">/// a symbol look up is done to see it is returns a specific reference type</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00058" /><CodeLine lineNumber="58"><Highlight kind="comment">/// to add to the comment stream.  This function returns Success if it adds</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00059" /><CodeLine lineNumber="59"><Highlight kind="comment">/// an operand to the MCInst and Fail otherwise.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
